


    [dir="${jdk_dir}"]

Install Java Development Kit (JDK).

required positional arguments with defaults:
    1.  JDK installation directory.
        Defaults to '${jdk_dir}'.

details:
    Note that yum installs to '/usr/lib/jvm/' on Fedora.
    Symlinks are defined in '/etc/alternatives/'.

